document.full_text: the mounted head of an endangered white rhinoceros and the stuffed remains of a highly endangered snow leopard, remnants of the fortune amassed and lost by an alaska real-estate titan, have been auctioned off to pay some of his debts, officials said on monday.
document.title: rhino head, snow leopard sold in u.s. auction
